'''庫爾提烏斯博物館'''（{{Lang-fr|Musée Curtius}}）是位於[[比利時|比利時]][[瓦隆大区|瓦隆地區]]城市[[列日|列日]]的一座[[博物館|博物館]]，也是瓦隆的主要遺產。博物館建築修建於1597年至1610年時期，最早是一位富商的豪宅。<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.visitbelgium.com/index.php?mact=News,cntnt01,print,0&cntnt01articleid=14&cntnt01showtemplate=false&cntnt01returnid=109|title = The Grand Curtius in Liege|accessdate = 2016-03-01|author = |date = |publisher = Visit Belgium|archive-date = 2019-09-23|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190923173953/http://visitbelgium.com/index.php?mact=News,cntnt01,print,0&cntnt01articleid=14&cntnt01showtemplate=false&cntnt01returnid=109|dead-url = no}}</ref>在經過耗資5000萬歐元的修繕之後，新的“'''大库尔提乌斯博物館'''”（{{lang|fr|Le Grand Curtius}}）於2009年3月重新開放。<ref>{{Cite news|url = http://ec.europa.eu/regional_policy/index.cfm/en/projects/belgium/newly-refurbished-curtius-museum-reopens-to-the-public|title = Newly refurbished Curtius museum reopens to the public|last = |first = |date = 2009-12-17|work = European Commission|accessdate = 2016-03-01|archive-date = 2019-11-21|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191121122903/https://ec.europa.eu/regional_policy/index.cfm/en/projects/belgium/newly-refurbished-curtius-museum-reopens-to-the-public|dead-url = no}}</ref>
